        </pre>
        
        <!-- Beta Banner -->
        <div class="bg-orange-500/20 border border-orange-500/50 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 mb-8 inline-block">
          <span class="text-orange-400 font-semibold">üöÄ Beta Now Available!</span>
          <span class="text-orange-300 ml-2">v0.9.0-beta.1 - MVP Feature Complete</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Automate Your Entire<br />
          <span class="text-blue-400">Developer Workflow</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Intelligent time tracking, cross-platform focus mode, and custom ritual automation. 
          Built by developers, for developers. Zero cloud dependencies.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/getting-started" 
             class="px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">
            Try Beta Now
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/ferg-cod3s/rune" 
             class="px-8 py-3 border border-gray-600 text-gray-300 hover:text-white hover:border-gray-400 font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">
            View on GitHub
          </a>
          <a href="/docs" 
             class="px-8 py-3 border border-gray-600 text-gray-300 hover:text-white hover:border-gray-400 font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">
            Documentation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Why Rune?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Built for developers who want to automate their workflow without sacrificing control.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
        <div class="text-blue-400 text-2xl mb-4">‚è±Ô∏è</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Intelligent Time Tracking</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Automatic project detection via Git, package.json, go.mod. Session persistence across restarts.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
        <div class="text-blue-400 text-2xl mb-4">üîï</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Cross-Platform Focus Mode</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Automatic Do Not Disturb on macOS, Windows, and Linux. 6+ desktop environments supported.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
        <div class="text-blue-400 text-2xl mb-4">ü§ñ</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Ritual Automation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Custom commands that run when you start/stop work. YAML configuration with error handling.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
        <div class="text-blue-400 text-2xl mb-4">üîÑ</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Migration Tools</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Import data from Watson and Timewarrior with project mapping and dry-run preview.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
        <div class="text-blue-400 text-2xl mb-4">üìä</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Beautiful Reporting</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Colored CLI output with themes. Daily/weekly summaries and project breakdowns.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
        <div class="text-blue-400 text-2xl mb-4">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Privacy-First</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          All data stored locally. No cloud dependencies. Optional telemetry with full transparency.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Quick Start Section -->
  <div class="bg-gray-800/30 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Quick Start</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Get up and running in minutes</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto">
        <div class="text-gray-400 mb-2"># Install via curl (macOS/Linux)</div>
        <div class="text-green-400">$ curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ferg-cod3s/rune/main/install.sh | bash</div>
        <br/>
        <div class="text-gray-400 mb-2"># Or via Homebrew</div>
        <div class="text-green-400">$ brew install --cask ferg-cod3s/tap/rune</div>
        <br/>
        <div class="text-gray-400 mb-2"># Interactive setup</div>
        <div class="text-green-400">$ rune init --guided</div>
        <br/>
        <div class="text-gray-400 mb-2"># Start tracking (auto-detects project, enables DND)</div>
        <div class="text-green-400">$ rune start</div>
        <br/>
        <div class="text-gray-400 mb-2"># View your daily report</div>
        <div class="text-green-400">$ rune report today</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/getting-started" 
           class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">
          View detailed installation guide ‚Üí
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
